caption.p: Infection rates (mosquitoes per 1000)/trap/week of Aedes aegypti with Chikungunya (CHIKV), dengue (DENV) or Zika (ZIKV) viruses in (A, B) two untreated and (C, D) two treated communities in southern Puerto Rico in 2014 and 2016: (A) Arboleda, (B) Playa, (C) La Margarita, and (D) Villodas.
